m, you learn more about the life and career of Arabella, and the challenges she faced as a woman navigating her scientific career.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425350/extras/3f66fa88951929204f0567c4cb67424c.poster.avif?t=1763652620\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425350/extras/3f66fa88951929204f0567c4cb67424c.webm?t=1763652620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425350/extras/3f66fa88951929204f0567c4cb67424c.mp4?t=1763652620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Botany Manor offers a relaxing and peaceful environment, feel free to stop and smell the roses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425350/extras/c62bbf3894eced4c682c688ad563fbd0.poster.avif?t=1763652620\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425350/extras/c62bbf3894eced4c682c688ad563fbd0.webm?t=1763652620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425350/extras/c62bbf3894eced4c682c688ad563fbd0.mp4?t=1763652620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425350/extras/219660d25e5b705a18c0312c53c65748.avif?t=1763652620\" width=630 height=64 /></span>",
